    "Political and legal advancements The unprecedented paceIn late October 2023, U.S. President Joe Biden's \"Executive Order on Safe, Secure, and Trustworthy Artificial Intelligence\" marked a pivotal move in signaling the will to manage the risks and promises of AI [148]."
